---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Demo 1: ZigZag Timeline">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Style 1: The Zig-Zag Vertical</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-16">A classic branching timeline. Elements alternate sides on a desktop to break up vertical monotony, but collapse gracefully to the left side on a phone.</p>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- The vertical spine -->
      <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-zinc-800 md:-translate-x-1/2 z-0"></div>
      
      <!-- Event 1 (Left Side) -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mb-16 w-full group">
        <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12"></div>
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 border-4 border-zinc-950 md:-translate-x-1/2 -ms-2.5 md:ms-0 z-10 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform shadow-lg"></div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-5/12 pl-12 md:pl-0">
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 font-bold mb-2 block tracking-widest text-sm">2022</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">The Prototype</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Initial build using basic physics calculations. Failed spectacularly under pressure, providing crucial fluid dynamic data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Event 2 (Right Side) -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center justify-between mb-16 w-full group">
        <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12"></div>
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border-4 border-zinc-950 md:-translate-x-1/2 -ms-2.5 md:ms-0 z-10 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform shadow-lg"></div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-5/12 pl-12 md:pr-0 md:text-right">
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors inline-block text-left w-full shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold mb-2 block tracking-widest text-sm">2023</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">Reinforcements</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Upgraded the entire launch mechanism. Swapped standard piping for high-density PVC, allowing for double the internal pressure limit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Event 3 (Left Side) -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mb-16 w-full group">
        <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12"></div>
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500 border-4 border-zinc-950 md:-translate-x-1/2 -ms-2.5 md:ms-0 z-10 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform shadow-lg"></div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-5/12 pl-12 md:pl-0">
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-purple-500 font-bold mb-2 block tracking-widest text-sm">2024</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-2">The Final Form</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">System perfected. Consistent launches over 300+ feet with zero catastrophic system failures.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
